{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-js","path":"/blog/ducky-one-2-mini-mac-problem","webpackCompilationHash":"7a91b0c995c42dd36e1a","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"ducky-one-2-mini-mac-problem"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ducky One 2 Mini Mac Problem","date":"August 8th, 2020","hero_image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5098039215686274,"src":"/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/0ab32/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg","srcSet":"/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/a6209/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 375w,\n/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/849fc/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 750w,\n/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/0ab32/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 1500w,\n/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/656ff/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 2250w,\n/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/51810/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 3000w,\n/static/37346eb820052a8c74a997ecd69f578d/b0f20/juan-gomez-kt-wA0GDFq8-unsplash.jpg 4928w","sizes":"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px"}}}},"html":"<p>Problem: Keyboard keep shutting down (not respond) for a random time on Mac OS</p>\n<p>Root Cause: Conflict with Mac OS driver, happens every osx check for update</p>\n<p>Solution: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>press Fn + Alt + P for 3 s</li>\n<li>number key and A~F will light up</li>\n<li>type \"05AC024F\" (Change the VID and PID which apple authorised)</li>\n<li>then restart the keyboard by unplug and plug</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Reference:\n<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/MechanicalKeyboards/comments/bujqr3/ducky_one_2_mini_on_mac_issues_anyone/\">https://www.reddit.com/r/MechanicalKeyboards/comments/bujqr3/ducky<em>one</em>2<em>mini</em>on<em>mac</em>issues_anyone/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://linustechtips.com/main/topic/1035569-issue-with-ducky-one-2-mini-macos/\">https://linustechtips.com/main/topic/1035569-issue-with-ducky-one-2-mini-macos/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HcccRek/status/1215671807723753472\">https://twitter.com/HcccRek/status/1215671807723753472</a></p>"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"ducky-one-2-mini-mac-problem"}}}